author: amol
msg: In setCellFormula(String) the Ptg stack in FormulaRecord is cleared before filling it with new values. Prior to this fix, repeated calls to setCellFormula would keep accumulating Ptgs in the stack although only the topmost "size" number of Ptgs would ever be used.
